webResources.textAttributionSnippet: (en) Portrait of the Clentist Christian Gabriel Ekberg Broken from Saint Anna, he came to Lköpping in 1832. Over time, he became a master with a workshop in the city’s neighbourhood of Sankt Lars 38, within the present neighbourhood of Braxen. From 1836 until his death in 1882 he was married to Ulrika Eleonora Sofia Willén - https://www.europeana.eu/item/73/S_OM_photo_OMEA0001240052. Östergötlands museum - http://digitaltmuseum.se/021017430140. Public Domain Mark - http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/mark/1.0/
